cmd.do('''
hide all
show cartoon, all
color grey, (name C*)
color red, (name O*)
color blue, (name N*)
color yellow,(name S*) 

set sphere_scale, 0.25, (all)
set line_width, 2.5
show sp, organic or polymer.nucleic
show lines, organic or polymer.nucleic

set sphere_scale, 0.5, (solvent)
zoom organic
show sphere, solvent
rotate [1,1,1], 180, all
png ~/structure_bio/HW1/all_components.png, width=10cm, dpi=300, ray=1
''')
